<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7906267>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Eurhaphidophora apicoexcisa sp. nov., male (holotype): head with anterior part of pronotum in dorsal (A), lateral (B) and frontal (C) views; abdominal apex in dorsal (D), lateral (E), posteroventral (F), posterior (G), posterolateral (H) and ventral (I) views." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7906267/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7906271>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Eurhaphidophora apicoexcisa sp. nov., male (paratypes), posteromedian process on ninth abdominal tergite in dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7906271/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7906273>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Eurhaphidophora apicoexcisa sp. nov., female (paratype): abdominal apex in dorsal (A) and lateral (B) views; subgenital plate in ventral view (C); ovipositor in lateral view (D)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7906273/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7906279>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Eurhaphidophora apicoexcisa sp. nov. (paratypes) in-situ: male in lateral (A) and dorsal (B) views; female with part of male in lateral view (C)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7906279/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

